# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: runtime
domain: quest
scope: quest.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for quest.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers quest visibility,
progress rendering,
branching state,
completion/failure state,
historical quest reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- quest identity must resolve
- objective basis must resolve
- progress basis must resolve
- completion/failure mode must be valid
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid quest identity
- invalid objective basis
- invalid progress scope
- invalid completion path
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish progress,
branching,
completion,
failure,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- quest runtime scope is explicit
- progress-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
